Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:24.05,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,這裏請交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:26.26,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,隊長 請聯絡總部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:27.30,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:32.80,Default,Black,0,0,0,,莫非還覺得自己能做什麼？半個嘉依卡小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:35.81,Default,Red,0,0,0,,遺體 還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.39,0:03:40.06,Default,Black,0,0,0,,啊啦 虧我還放了你一馬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:44.88,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:47.74,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,你們打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:50.32,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:08.95,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:14.18,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 我現在要拋棄亂破師的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:16.70,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,和你不再是兄妹關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.67,0:04:19.98,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,兄長 別走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:23.98,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,芙蕾多妮卡 我要和你結下契約
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:38.56,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,托魯 吃下我的肉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:40.17,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,不然會死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:56.85,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,芙蕾多妮卡 我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:02.23,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,我要擊敗賈茲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:04.10,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托魯 我 同行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:13.98,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,保重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.69,0:05:23.54,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托魯 我 同行 希望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:25.36,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.17,0:05:29.27,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:32.27,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:34.78,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,辛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在你看來朕的舉止很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:40.52,Default,Shin,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:47.19,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,朕過去發明的技術 不過是深邃魔法研究的皮毛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:50.62,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,只要將此居城與天上的<奇伊>連接
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:55.49,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,全大陸的思念將不斷涌入朕體內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:06:00.39,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,朕要做的事仍然堆積如山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:24.07,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:29.56,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,賈茲皇帝復活？不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:32.08,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,賈茲想再次發動戰亂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:36.13,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,吸取大陸人民心中高漲的恐懼與絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:38.66,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,作為自己的魔力源
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:41.67,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,哈爾特根公王已被殺害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:47.52,Default,Matheus,0,0,0,,經城內打探 哈爾特根公國的軍備 根本不值一提
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:53.44,Default,Matheus,0,0,0,,是黑嘉依卡散播謠言 哄騙哈爾特根公王發動戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:55.76,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,都是賈茲安排的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:07:00.39,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,原來如此 此事我會在議會上轉告赫德拉將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:01.65,Default,Red,0,0,0,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.06,0:07:06.36,Default,Red,0,0,0,,遺體 還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:07.92,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,遺體已經沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:12.18,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,這傢伙吃了所有的遺體 復活了賈茲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:13.76,Default,Red,0,0,0,,父親 復活？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:18.69,Default,Black,0,0,0,,正好 把你們也做成人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:23.62,Default,Black,0,0,0,,她們也跟艾琳娜伊琳娜一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:26.25,Default,Black,0,0,0,,都是我可愛的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:29.71,Default,Black,0,0,0,,那半個你們拿去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.21,0:07:32.00,Default,Black,0,0,0,,我要跟紅色的玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:39.13,Default,David,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:40.61,Default,Fyodor,0,0,0,,賈茲復活？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:42.82,Default,Aide,0,0,0,,是的 要攻擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.03,0:07:45.72,Default,Fyodor,0,0,0,,不 立刻返回
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:46.22,Default,Aide,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.83,Default,Fyodor,0,0,0,,僅憑我軍無力抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:51.56,Default,Fyodor,0,0,0,,直接進攻 會正中賈茲下懷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:00.45,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,芙蕾多妮卡 無論如何也要進去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.07,0:08:02.71,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,隨便哪都行 拆個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:06.70,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,結界？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:11.79,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,顯現吧 爆破消散之物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:13.08,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,<破坏者>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:17.50,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:20.79,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,好 芙蕾多妮卡 繼續玩命轟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:28.10,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,居然跟到這裏 值得誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:29.85,Default,Shin,0,0,0,,此人請交給我處理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:36.48,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,芙蕾多妮卡 衝進去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:48.84,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,這就是賈茲說的思念吸收裝置<奇伊>？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:54.49,Default,Zita,0,0,0,,看來只要其中一台啟動 其他的都會陸續激活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:57.80,Default,Matheus,0,0,0,,估計要跟下降的那台連接
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:00.69,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,全部激活之前 還剩多少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:05.24,Default,Matheus,0,0,0,,具體我不清楚 但恐怕 今晚就會完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:10.14,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,那樣一來 我們今後的思念都會歸賈茲所有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:12.29,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,無力回天了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:27.84,Default,David,0,0,0,,和你哥和白丫頭去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:29.54,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,去對付賈茲了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.17,0:09:37.08,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,吾即為鋼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:40.59,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,吾鋼故無畏 吾鋼故無惑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:44.43,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,若敵當前 便捨棄一切顧慮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:47.71,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,吾乃滅敵之兇器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.01,0:09:49.05,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,鐵血轉化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:01.29,Default,Shin,0,0,0,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:09.83,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,思念吸收 絕對阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:18.69,Default,Shin,0,0,0,,不當亂破師了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:21.02,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,辛哥 別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:31.11,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,芙蕾多妮卡 別出手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:36.43,Default,Shin,0,0,0,,終於理解我的話了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:38.72,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,跟你無關 我自己決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:18.69,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:29.09,Default,Shin,0,0,0,,很好 托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你不適合當亂破師
