Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:57.60,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,尼克拉 慢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:19.16,Default,Black,0,0,0,,顯現吧 肆虐之物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:21.12,Default,Black,0,0,0,,<爆风>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:25.04,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,保護之物 消散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:26.80,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,<破坏者>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:45.11,Default,Black,0,0,0,,別忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:47.87,Default,Black,0,0,0,,我達成了目的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:52.58,Default,Black,0,0,0,,復活父親的 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:54.41,Default,Red,0,0,0,,那又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:02.21,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,幹掉黑色的了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:07.59,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,效果 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:14.86,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:19.14,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,顯現吧 迴響探測之物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:20.97,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,<探索者>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.19,0:13:34.98,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,賈茲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.10,0:13:43.14,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,朕活了五百年的歲月 是依靠魔法不斷更換身體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:45.83,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,於是有了結論
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:49.30,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,人類總是在追求戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:56.58,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,為憤怒 為憎恨 為愛 人會殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:14:03.48,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,一百年後 兩百年後 人類只要略有機會仍會互相廝殺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:07.50,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,你現在 手中拿著何物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:11.15,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,你證明了人類的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:16.66,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,既然如此喜歡戰鬥 就為朕所用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:17.41,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:22.03,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,朕觀察著你們的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.33,0:14:28.20,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,朕大部分身軀 是由你背著 由你抱著送來這裏的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:32.55,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,值得誇讚 做得非常出色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:44.89,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:49.84,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:12.17,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,人類的心中都有殺意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:18.75,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,只要有針尖大小的契機 殺意便會輕易支配內心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:22.14,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:52.78,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,現在你的心中 充滿了殺意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:57.26,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,你無法抑制 對朕兵刃相向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:16:03.64,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,正是這樣的人 能回應朕的意圖 更好地完成工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:05.97,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,為朕所用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:12.48,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,你的胡話 沒人想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:17.40,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,活了五百年 就這點本事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:19.52,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:22.91,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,再回一遍娘胎吧 混小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:41.05,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,你這人實在有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:43.01,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,但到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:45.30,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,<护盾>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:53.67,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,嗯 357號嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:55.86,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,吾之仗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:01.28,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.09,0:17:03.67,Default,Niva,0,0,0,,瞄準目標確認
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:06.16,Default,Niva,0,0,0,,目標是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.31,0:17:14.70,Default,Niva,0,0,0,,拒絕鎖定目標
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:15.66,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:17.62,Default,Niva,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 無法消除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:30.39,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,妮娃 為何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:33.19,Default,Niva,0,0,0,,我 有人格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:41.36,Default,Niva,0,0,0,,請裝填彈藥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:43.75,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,魔法思念料 枯竭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:48.07,Default,Niva,0,0,0,,從魔法思念料消耗形態 轉為記憶消除形態嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:48.83,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:52.58,Default,Niva,0,0,0,,確認目標
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:54.76,Default,Niva,0,0,0,,要破壞目標嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:57.15,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯 我 父親 憑悼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:17:59.09,Default,Niva,0,0,0,,攻擊魔法 啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:04.05,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,Zikra, azulwa, istatu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:06.47,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,顯現吧 壓縮潰倒之物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:08.94,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,<奇迹>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:38.29,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,兄長…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:40.54,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:52.01,Default,Zita,0,0,0,,基列特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:55.23,Default,Zita,0,0,0,,上空的航天要塞停了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:56.88,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,那亂破師做的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:14.45,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:18.00,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,你做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:19.21,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.77,0:19:25.84,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,醒醒 嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:30.52,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,求你了 別丟下我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:31.68,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:43.62,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,戰後五年 死後仍威脅著大陸的禁斷皇帝賈茲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:48.85,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,利用嘉依卡收集遺體 借助魔法復活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:53.54,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,但不久便自毀 與航天要塞一起消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:59.51,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,同時確認多名疑似其女嘉依卡的少女死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.39,0:20:03.00,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,賈茲遺留的機子也已經回收
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:10.01,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,至此 禁斷皇帝與其女——嘉依卡一案 可以斷定終結
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:14.89,Default,Fyodor,0,0,0,,基列特機關長 本次任務真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:18.69,Default,Fyodor,0,0,0,,代我感謝尼克拉隊的辛勞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:20.85,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:31.31,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,康拉德參謀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.61,0:20:33.53,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,啊 不必拘束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:37.54,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,這個稱呼我哈似乎不習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:41.66,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,基列特機關長 不考慮稍微休息兩天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:45.04,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,不 如您所見 工作堆積如山
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.19,0:20:51.06,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,雖然劍換成了筆 想揮灑自如也不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:54.93,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,機關長 您的傷如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:59.43,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,沒什麼 這程度也就算個擦傷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:01.94,Default,Gillete,0,0,0,,對我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:15.96,Default,Red,0,0,0,,火大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:17.41,Default,Red,0,0,0,,門 何時修復
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.98,0:21:19.62,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,兄長修之前 修不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:21.02,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,我不修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:24.03,Default,Red,0,0,0,,探病禮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:25.25,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,又麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:26.92,Default,Red,0,0,0,,何物執筆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:29.65,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,亂破師兄妹熾熱的愛情故事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:31.02,Default,Red,0,0,0,,執筆結束？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.32,0:21:33.52,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,不 這只是個續章
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:36.23,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,兩人的愛之旅程才剛要開始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:38.78,Default,Red,0,0,0,,白丫頭 何處
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.08,0:21:40.52,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,跟兄長散步去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.29,0:21:43.34,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,今天貌似狀態不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.57,0:21:56.75,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,看著點 小心腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.55,0:22:00.58,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,謝謝

